where they were aimed.  The dispersion of the bombs is so wide that even if the original target 
were outside a populated area, many bombs fell amid the houses.&#8221;, in Meron Rapoport.  &#8220;What 
lies beneath&#8221;, Haaretz, 8 September 2006 http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/760246.html 
(retrieved on 8 November 2006).<b> 
